reviewText: Great product and I love this band buy this DVD now if you're a Muse fan! You won't regret it.

amazing gig full of energy with a really wonderful vibe and crowd and absolutely breathtaking setlist. even thoung it's not the most recent thing it's still worth watching. and if you're a real fan the extras will make you happy!
It's a good concert, but the quality of the Dvds isn't too great. The feeling is kind of amateurish as well.
